node.text: That dress is gorgeous! The peacock 🦚 print it 😍

Finally made her bed and had to document. Haven’t made it again since this photo was taken. .
.
.
Let’s all remember that a photo is one moment in time. Her room is never this clean. And I am usually covered in children with sticky hands asking me questions about how gummy bears are made or how long are our intestines. I rarely have the right answers. Although I nailed it with knowing alveoli today. .
.
.
Dress @simoneirani 
Earrings @houseofrajput
If only you could see the state we get into at home!
@shoplustre thank you! It’s like copper/ rose gold color. Hoping she can use it for a while.
I LOVE that bed. So fab. And of course, any tidying up must be documented.
@elyseandi_official 😅 thank you. Some days better than others
@ampliobeauty for a brief moment before the masness
Haha love it. Clean room and looking glam.
@indiibreeze think she’ll mind if I sneak in here to do mine?
@instantgoddess thank you! Did the whole room according to her love of pink. Next week she tells me she likes green beat. 🤷🏼‍♀️🤦🏼‍♀️
Haha their rooms are a mess the second they are clean. Given up tidying up after them!
@templecandles let’s hope so! Cause I’m wrong a lot.
🤣🤣 Only remember the times you were right!
That dress is gorgeous! The peacock 🦚 print it 😍
